id":25794,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你推幾多組幾多下?</blockquote><br />\n我推10下一組<br />\n一組後休息2分鐘<br />\n再推<br />\n推夠4組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11af3949947a3544a8980815690970cea26e12a","tid":25794,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係你前臂唔夠 樣樣都練下 二三頭 背膊 好快就唔洗用到前臂</blockquote><br />\n二頭做緊3set 1set 15下<br />\n<img src=\"http://mypullzone.fitnessworld1.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/hammer-curls-300x225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmypullzone.fitnessworld1.netdna-cdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F04%2Fhammer-curls-300x225.jpg&h=5aaee804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三頭做緊3組, 一組15下<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.blastyourbiceps.org/affiliates/photos/dumbbell-tricep-extension.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blastyourbiceps.org%2Faffiliates%2Fphotos%2Fdumbbell-tricep-extension.jpg&h=2df5014a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問以下動作是否背膊???<br />\n做緊15下 一組, 做3組<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.building-muscle101.com/images/dumbbell-workout-for-back-main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.building-muscle101.com%2Fimages%2Fdumbbell-workout-for-back-main.jpg&h=886440e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef05c91fd61daf4b3fc076c3e2f246f4e14ce57f","tid":25794,"uid":26522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁係你前臂唔夠 樣樣都練下 二三頭 背膊 好快就唔洗用到前臂</blockquote><br />\n二頭做緊3set 1set 15下<br />\n<img src=\"http://mypullzone.fitnessworld1.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/hammer-curls-300x225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmypullzone.fitnessworld1.netdna-cdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F04%2Fhammer-curls-300x225.jpg&h=5aaee804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三頭做緊3組, 一組15下<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.blastyourbiceps.org/affiliates/photos/dumbbell-tricep-extension.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blastyourbiceps.org%2Faffiliates%2Fphotos%2Fdumbbell-tricep-extension.jpg&h=2df5014a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問以下動作是否背膊???<br />\n做緊15下 一組, 做3組<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.building-muscle101.com/images/dumbbell-workout-for-back-main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.building-muscle101.com%2Fimages%2Fdumbbell-workout-for-back-main.jpg&h=886440e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新手就玩下機先啦，怕你肌肉未習慣，會拉傷"},{"pid":"faab0b63476dd38eee684bb232e3b7f3305bcf9a","tid":25794,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:26:09.000Z","msg":"最緊要姿勢正確，推得輕冇人會笑<br />\n<br />\n推得重又用錯姿勢用錯力我就細聲笑喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5a07f05d381b5e6c185b8b3bde8d1e3991c6cd","tid":25794,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要姿勢正確，推得輕冇人會笑<br />\n<br />\n推得重又用錯姿勢用錯力我就細聲笑喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知有冇推錯<br />\n有冇網上教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff6c098b32b899ae6f2a7185841546b1737bdd5","tid":25794,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你推幾多組幾多下?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我推10下一組<br />\n<br />\n一組後休息2分鐘<br />\n<br />\n再推<br />\n<br />\n推夠4組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推果時前臂有無酸軟 , 如果感到酸軟代表發錯力"},{"pid":"32db2d2fba5bebc042f25e7312d75646c8dde39d","tid":25794,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問以下動作是否背膊???<br />\n<br />\n做緊15下 一組, 做3組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.building-muscle101.com/images/dumbbell-workout-for-back-main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.building-muscle101.com%2Fimages%2Fdumbbell-workout-for-back-main.jpg&h=886440e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做背 , 拉上時手臂要貼腰 , 放下時要hold住慢落 , 做果時如 feel 到尾龍骨酸就要停, 代表發錯力或啞鈴太重"},{"pid":"42848f5d2fb195a728f052cc25546f3498686bf1","tid":25794,"uid":44466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩啦<br />\n你永遠不會成功.jpg"},{"pid":"c47c4cacf2454df9591851b3e9fb934b90a96345","tid":25794,"uid":44466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩啦<br />\n你永遠不會成功.jpg"}]}